			<div class="content" id="post-content-2651329">
									

<p>So I originally wrote this as an entry for the <a href="/d-class-contest">D-class contest</a>, but alas, twasn’t meant to be.</p>
<p>My undying gratitude to <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2039383); return false;">MrWrong</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eta-carinae" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2110706); return false;">Eta Carinae</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/erazm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2819735); return false;">Erazm</a></span> and <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/el-jimeiro" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2835692); return false;">El Jimeiro</a></span> for some excellent feedback, as well as to <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dexanote" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(481882); return false;">Dexanote</a></span> for providing feedback and answering my contest-related questions.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Spoilers</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Hide</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>I was tempted to call this <em>Soylent D</em>, but that would have spoiled the whole ending for those who got that reference. Hence, <em>Budget Cuts</em>.</p>
</div>
